<!DOCTYPE html><html><head><meta charset="utf-8"><style>body{font-family:Arial,sans-serif;max-width:600px;margin:0 auto;padding:20px;color:#333}.hdr{background:#2d6a4f;color:#fff;padding:20px;text-align:center;border-radius:8px 8px 0 0}.cnt{background:#f9f9f9;padding:30px;border:1px solid #ddd;border-top:none;border-radius:0 0 8px 8px}.btn{display:inline-block;padding:12px 24px;background:#2d6a4f;color:#fff!important;text-decoration:none;border-radius:6px;margin:16px 0}.ftr{text-align:center;padding:20px;color:#999;font-size:12px}.code{font-size:28px;letter-spacing:4px;font-weight:bold;color:#2d6a4f;padding:12px;background:#e8f5e9;border-radius:4px;text-align:center;margin:20px 0}</style></head><body><div class="hdr"><h1>Orchids</h1><p>Low Stock Alert</p></div><div class="cnt"><p>Hello,</p><p>The following products are below reorder level:</p><table style="width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;margin:16px 0"><tr style="background:#2d6a4f;color:#fff"><th style="padding:8px;text-align:left">Product</th><th style="padding:8px;text-align:right">Current Stock</th><th style="padding:8px;text-align:right">Reorder Level</th></tr>{{#each products}}<tr style="border-bottom:1px solid #ddd"><td style="padding:8px">{{this.name}}</td><td style="padding:8px;text-align:right">{{this.stockQty}}</td><td style="padding:8px;text-align:right">{{this.reorderLevel}}</td></tr>{{/each}}</table><p>Please take action to replenish inventory.</p></div><div class="ftr"><p>Orchids B2B Platform - Automated Message</p></div></body></html>
